parameters: there is no doubt that this is the main source of the outbreak.
「As I thought, let's annihilate what's here.
That way, the overall numbers will calm down.」
「Why don't we go home for today...?」
「No, I'm fine. I'll just annihilate them.」
If you don't treat the wound from earlier, it will remain, you know?」
and get back on our feet for today.
「After all that... my chest hurts a little.」
「Miss Helena, there's no need for mercy to the monsters.」
「Now then, I hope this will make it easier to travel
to and from the eastern city.」
\F[h6s]\FF[r1s]\AA[N]In spite of the depths of the cave,
man-made things like broken bottles and parts of books caught my eye.
「I wonder... if there were other people besides us...」
「I wonder if that person is ok?
I hope they managed to escape...」
\N[5] felt uncomfortable with the brand new traces of human presence.
Nothing that can identify the person is left,
but it might be good to keep it in mind.
